Detailed Description

Object wrapper for mpq_t.

This class is a wrapper around the mpq structure and functions from the gmp.d interface. Arithmetic operations like add, mult, etc allocate a new object and call the low-level gmp function. The underlying mpq_t struct is public and can be directly passed to the gmp.d interface.
